\[CloseCurlyQuote]t add more material until everyone is solid on those. On \
the other hand, I don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t know what to \[LongDash] in terms of \
things I could say or additional problems I could write up \[LongDash] to \
help make those more solid. So I have just chosen more Spivak problems.\
\>", "Text",
